<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════ PRIVACY POLICY ═══════════════════════════════════ -->
<section class="privacy-section">
  <div class="wrap">
    
    <div class="privacy-header">
      <h1><span>PRIVACY POLICY</span><br>LICA-Bildirim Işığı ve Fener</h1>
      <div class="last-updated">Last updated: March 2026</div>
      <div class="developer">Developer: SAEY Yazılım</div>
      <div class="contact">
        Contact: <a href="mailto:saeyazilim@gmail.com">saeyazilim@gmail.com</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="privacy-card">
      
      <!-- Introduction -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <p>This Privacy Policy describes how the LICA-Bildirim Işığı ve Fener (com.phone.ligthcase) application ("App") collects, uses, and protects your information. By using the App, you agree to this policy.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 1. DATA COLLECTED -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">01</span> DATA COLLECTED</h2>
        <p>LICA-Bildirim Işığı ve Fener does not store personal user data on our servers and does not sell data to third parties. The App processes only the following:</p>
        
        <p><strong class="highlight">a) On-Device Data (local, never sent to our servers)</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>- Notification preferences (which apps trigger flash/glow)</li>
          <li>- Flash pattern, color, and schedule settings</li>
          <li>- Premium activation status (yes/no)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <p><strong class="highlight">b) Firebase Realtime Database (Google LLC)</strong></p>
        <ul>
          <li>- The activation code entered during premium unlock is verified against Firebase. Once verified, the code is deleted. No user identity, email address, or device identifier is sent to Firebase.</li>
          <li>- Firebase Privacy Policy: 
            <a href="https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy" target="_blank" style="color:var(--c);">https://firebase.google.com/support/privacy</a>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. PERMISSIONS AND PURPOSE -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">02</span> PERMISSIONS AND PURPOSE</h2>
        <p>The App uses the following Android permissions:</p>
        
        <div class="permission-group">
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To display glow animations over the lock screen.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">READ_PHONE_STATE</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To manage flash behavior during incoming calls.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">BIND_NOTIFICATION_LISTENER_SERVICE</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To trigger flash/glow when a notification arrives.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">CAMERA / FLASHLIGHT</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To use the camera flash as a notification light.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">INTERNET / ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ For premium code verification via Firebase.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">VIBRATE</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To support notifications in vibration mode.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">WAKE_LOCK / USE_FULL_SCREEN_INTENT / DISABLE_KEYGUARD</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To display glow animations while the screen is off.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">FOREGROUND_SERVICE / FOREGROUND_SERVICE_SPECIAL_USE</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To run the glow overlay service in the background.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">POST_NOTIFICATIONS</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To send a test notification at the user's request.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="permission-item">
            <span class="permission-name">REQUEST_IGNORE_BATTERY_OPTIMIZATIONS</span>
            <span class="permission-desc">→ To prevent the background service from being killed by the system.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. THIRD-PARTY SERVICES -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">03</span> THIRD-PARTY SERVICES</h2>
        <p>The App uses only Firebase Realtime Database (Google LLC), and only during the premium activation flow. No third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking SDKs are included.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. CHILDREN'S PRIVACY -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">04</span> CHILDREN'S PRIVACY</h2>
        <p>The App is not directed at children under 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. DATA SECURITY -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">05</span> DATA SECURITY</h2>
        <p>User preferences are stored locally in SharedPreferences on the device. Premium activation data is transmitted over Firebase's secure infrastructure. No personally identifiable information is processed.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 6. CHANGES TO THIS POLICY -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">06</span> CHANGES TO THIS POLICY</h2>
        <p>This policy may be updated from time to time. For significant changes, a notice will be posted on the app store listing. The updated policy is effective from the date it is published on this page.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 7. CONTACT -->
      <div class="policy-section">
        <h2><span class="section-number">07</span> CONTACT</h2>
        <p>For questions about this privacy policy:</p>
        <div class="note">
          <strong>📧 saeyazilim@gmail.com</strong>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Footer -->
      <div class="policy-footer">
        <a href="index.html">🏠 Home</a>
        <span class="separator">•</span>
        <a href="#">⬆️ Back to Top</a>
        <span class="separator">•</span>
        <a href="mailto:saeyazilim@gmail.com">📧 Email</a>
        <div style="margin-top:20px; font-size:12px;">
          © 2026 LICA-Notification Light · SAEY Yazılım
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════════════════════ FOOTER ═══════════════════════════════════ -->
<footer>
  <div class="wrap">
    <p style="margin-bottom:8px;">
      <a href="index.html" class="logo" style="font-size:15px;">LIGHT<em style="color:rgba(0,229,255,0.35);font-style:normal;">CASE</em></a>
    </p>
